Gin and Postgres

handler/ → for HTTP handlers/controllers

model/ → for domain models and structs

config/ → for environment and database config

utils/ → for reusable helper functions

router/ → for route setup
middleware -> for intercept HTTP requests to perform tasks like authentication, authorization, error handling, and logging before reaching the final handler
main.go → as entry point


create environment variable at root .env and add the following variable
POSTGRES_USER=user
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=password
POSTGRES_DB=gin_db
DB_HOST=db
DB_PORT=5432
JWT_SECRET=yourSuperSecretKey
DB_URL=postgres://user:password@db:5432/gin_db?sslmode=disable
